Package: LINTULcassava
Type: Package
Title: LINTUL CASSAVA crop growth simulation model
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2026-01-09
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: litedown, deSolve
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0-10)
VignetteBuilder: litedown 
Author: Guillaume Ezui, Rob van den Beuken, Joy Adiele, Peter Leffelaar, Tom Schut
Maintainer: Robert Hijmans <r.hijmans@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements a LINTUL crop growth simulation model for cassava described by <Ezui et al., 2018. Simulating drought impact and mitigation in cassava using the LINTUL model. Field Crops Research 219: 256-272>. The package contains a C++ implementation of the model as well as the R implementation in the scripts available here https://models.pps.wur.nl/index.php/lintulcassavanpk (2024-10-2100), with minor tweaks in the user interface to make it easier to use. 
License: EUPL
